{"tid":1605182,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有巴打癡咗線，背住我哋整咗個專門收集同整理連登行動post 嘅網站，以為冇人知？","createTime":"2019-09-30T08:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:12:04.000Z","uid":205482,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5f4c9354cb5ed60a2cb3990bcbeef59e38cf79","tid":1605182,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T08:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[突發] 整左個網站比大家睇香港人如何被濫暴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486628/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486628/</a><br />\n<br />\n【若水之夏】香港人真係痴撚線，100日內不斷進化<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579761</a> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme0w 巴打話發現好多人都唔知佢哋個 Website <a href=\"https://hkrev.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=db545f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/</a> 除左時序線之外仲有咩功能。現盡小弟綿力宣傳以下喺呢段時間佢哋個 Website update 咗啲乜嘢：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登行動Post集合:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/activity.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Factivity.php&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=2ecb061f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/activity.php</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港日程 (Support .ics format):<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=a3a16847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a></span><br />\n<br />\n上呢個網非常方便全港市民迅速睇到嚟緊有咩行動同日程，實為全新嘅行動、實用、資訊性、攻略post一覽。以後邊個再問行動post喺邊 / 熱門冇行動post / 置頂唔到實用post 嘅你哋，請上     <a href=\"https://hkrev.info/activity.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Factivity.php&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=2ecb061f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/activity.php</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你哋有需要置頂新嘅行動post，歡迎巴絲打自行開post，然後再喺連登洗地組度分享<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/HaQS-lgVgWXtn2fO2D6ALg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FHaQS-lgVgWXtn2fO2D6ALg&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=f1245b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/HaQS-lgVgWXtn2fO2D6ALg</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋會有手足幫你放喺新嘅「行動台」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞時序:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/news.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fnews.php&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=ca68fe04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/news.php</a><br />\n<br />\n運動時序 (中文版):<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=12c45aa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/</a><br />\n<br />\n運動時序 (英文版):<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fen%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=26564728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n運動時序 (日文版 正努力翻譯中):<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/ja/timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fja%2Ftimeline%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=93a0586c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/ja/timeline/</a><br />\n<br />\n警察濫暴事件薄 (中文版):<br />\n<a href=\"https://popo.dog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpopo.dog&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=b48a27ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://popo.dog</a><br />\n<br />\n警察濫暴事件簿 (英文版):<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.popo.dog\" 